BIT 3: Monitoring + Observability
👉 Goal: Know what's happening inside systems (very important for SRE)
🔹 Topics:
Monitoring vs Logging vs Tracing
Metrics (CPU, memory, latency)
Alerts & thresholds
🔹 Tools:
Prometheus
Grafana
ELK Stack
🔹 Key Concepts:
SLI (Service Level Indicator)
SLO (Service Level Objective)
SLA (Service Level Agreement)
🔹 What You Should Do:
Create dashboards
Set alerts for CPU spikes
Analyze logs during failures
